    {
      "bookmarkId": "32744340_3_1748-1835",
      "chapterUid": 3,
      "range": "1748-1835",
      "markText": "儿女是属于他们自己的。他们的现在，和他们的未来，都应由他们自己来设计。一个想用自己理想的模式塑造自己的孩子的父亲是愚蠢的，而且，可恶！另外作为一个父亲，应该尽量保持一点童心。",
      "totalCount": 2072,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=32744340&chapterUid=3&rangeStart=1748&rangeEnd=1835",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/4ad3227071f3a3944ade79a?chapterUid=3&rangeStart=1748&rangeEnd=1835"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "32744340_1_949-1021",
      "chapterUid": 1,
      "range": "949-1021",
      "markText": "有一回我不停地打嗝，他忽然把我叫到跟前，问我他吩咐我做的事做好了没有。我想了半天，他吩咐过我做什么事呀？我使劲地想。他哈哈大笑：“嗝不打了吧！”",
      "totalCount": 1515,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=32744340&chapterUid=1&rangeStart=949&rangeEnd=1021",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/4ad3227071f3a3944ade79a?chapterUid=1&rangeStart=949&rangeEnd=1021"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "32744340_1_452-521",
      "chapterUid": 1,
      "range": "452-521",
      "markText": "水不但于不自觉中成了我的一些小说的背景，并且也影响了我的小说的风格。水有时是汹涌澎湃的，但我们那里的水平常总是柔软的，平和的，静静地流着。",
      "totalCount": 1494,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=32744340&chapterUid=1&rangeStart=452&rangeEnd=521",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/4ad3227071f3a3944ade79a?chapterUid=1&rangeStart=452&rangeEnd=521"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "32744340_2_2809-2886",
      "chapterUid": 2,
      "range": "2809-2886",
      "markText": "我希望青年作家在起步的时候写得新一点，怪一点，朦胧一点，荒诞一点，狂妄一点，不要过早地归于平淡。三四十岁就写得很淡，那，到我这样的年龄，怕就什么也没有了。",
      "totalCount": 1394,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=32744340&chapterUid=2&rangeStart=2809&rangeEnd=2886",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/4ad3227071f3a3944ade79a?chapterUid=2&rangeStart=2809&rangeEnd=2886"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "32744340_1_2238-2295",
      "chapterUid": 1,
      "range": "2238-2295",
      "markText": "我父亲是个随便的人，比较有同情心，能平等待人。我十几岁时就和他对座饮酒，一起抽烟。他说：“我们是多年父子成兄弟。”",
      "totalCount": 1196,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=32744340&chapterUid=1&rangeStart=2238&rangeEnd=2295",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/4ad3227071f3a3944ade79a?chapterUid=1&rangeStart=2238&rangeEnd=2295"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "32744340_1_6991-7065",
      "chapterUid": 1,
      "range": "6991-7065",
      "markText": "我认为一篇小说是作者和读者共同创作的。作者写了，读者读了，创作过程才算完成。作者不能什么都知道，都写尽了。要留出余地，让读者去捉摸，去思索，去补充。",
      "totalCount": 1152,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=32744340&chapterUid=1&rangeStart=6991&rangeEnd=7065",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/4ad3227071f3a3944ade79a?chapterUid=1&rangeStart=6991&rangeEnd=7065"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "32744340_10_2018-2036",
      "chapterUid": 10,
      "range": "2018-2036",
      "markText": "凡事都是这样，要能适应、习惯、凑合。",
      "totalCount": 1150,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=32744340&chapterUid=10&rangeStart=2018&rangeEnd=2036",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/4ad3227071f3a3944ade79a?chapterUid=10&rangeStart=2018&rangeEnd=2036"
    },
    {
